{
  "id": "adv_event_2601_01_02",
  "title": "ドライブ\n行っちゃい\nましょ～！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "『仲良し三人組で、ドライブ行っちゃいましょ～！』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.7476640701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.9543306033
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "今日はこれから、この三人で\nmihoちゃんの車で、日帰り旅行に行ってきま～す！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.9543306033,
      "endTime": 12.6006793657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.7473459243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "三人で遊びに行くの、実は今日が初めてなのよね\n最近まで、全くそのことに気付いてなかったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7473459243,
      "endTime": 20.496189403499997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.7028562228
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事でもレッスン中でも、いつも一緒だものね\nむしろ、二人の顔を見ない日が全然ないって言うか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.7028562228,
      "endTime": 28.777572600099997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.9775724094
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "でも今日は、仕事ではないので\n普段はしないような話も、二人としたいなと思ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9775724094,
      "endTime": 34.9856674832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、二人とも車に乗って\nあまり遅くなってもいけないし、早めに出発するわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.1923341116,
      "endTime": 42.2093860946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.1923341116
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.4160527231
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "え～、mihoちゃんにだけ運転させるの悪いから\nkanaとfranちゃんも、交代で運転するよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.4160527231,
      "endTime": 50.4312226297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.631222439
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "大事な車を、この子達に運転させるなんて\n……いえ、少しでも動画の撮れ高を増やさないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.631222439,
      "endTime": 59.2446694375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "あ……ありがとう\nじゃあ、kanaとfranにも交代でお願いするわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.4380025229,
      "endTime": 65.3660976729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.4380025229
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい\nそれじゃあ、安全運転で出発しまーす！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.5794311207,
      "endTime": 71.2360976856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.5794311207
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_switch-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 71.4227644285
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "……せっかく一念発起して買った車なのに\n貴方達に運転させることになるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.4227644285,
      "endTime": 77.64714091619999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.4227644285
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "一念発起して買ったのがコレってさぁ……\nこんな昭和の暴走族みたいな車、逆によく見つけたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.8404742877,
      "endTime": 86.6178664844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.8404742877
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.8245333036
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "車高は低いし、フロントバンパーは張り出し過ぎだし\nしかもシートカバーが毛皮！　真っ赤！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.8245333036,
      "endTime": 94.9423562368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "マフラーも竹槍みたいに飛び出てるし\nこんなのに乗ったら、私の美的センスが狂いそう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.1290227891,
      "endTime": 101.7043967248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.1290227891
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "……二人して、人の車に言いたい放題\n文句があるなら、貴方達は歩いて追いかけてきなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.9110633534,
      "endTime": 109.1637844722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.9110633534
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……前に、葉ちゃんとドライブに行った時は\n運転もかわってくれたし、あんなに楽しかったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.3571175576,
      "endTime": 116.8257114411,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3933.3333332999982
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.3571175576
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.8257114411
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "……昔話をするようになったのは別にいいんだけど\n友達と私達を比べてばかりで、あれほんと腹立つのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.7923814774,
      "endTime": 127.13238143939999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.7923814774
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "ならさぁ……交代で運転することになった訳だし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.3457145056,
      "endTime": 132.5815422377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "どうせmihoは、ちんたら無難な運転だろうから\nkana達で、もっと面白くしてやらない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.7682089807,
      "endTime": 139.74229078309997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.7682089807
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_carinside-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 140.8222908022
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-05.m4a",
      "startTime": 141.0889584861
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "はい。……今は、kanaが運転中です\nmihoの車、車内もすっごい広くて快適なんですよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.8889584861,
      "endTime": 151.142813047,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-06.m4a",
          "delay": 54477.6976901
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cloth-01.m4a",
          "delay": 64677.697690100016
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_carinside-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 146.8666663487
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 146.8666663487
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_02-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、出発してしばらく経ったしおやつでも食べない？\n瑠依がオススメしてたグミに、こっちがコーヒーね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.3561463995,
      "endTime": 159.871202819,
      "sfxList": [
